#### Application of Damped Oscillations: Car suspension system

A car suspension supports the chassis (body) of the car onto the axles of the car wheels. A good suspension system should

1. _partially absorb the impact of a bump_ in the road for the comfort of the passengers
2. _return the car to equilibrium quickly_ so that it is ready to respond to other bumps on the road.

The desired degree of damping is near critical damping.

